epts\nsuch as selection techniques and luminosity functions are explained assuming\nessentially no prior knowledge. The intention is that this chapter can be used\nas an introduction to the observational study of high-redshift galaxies, as\nwell as providing a review of the latest results in this fast-moving research\nfield up to the end of 2011.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 May 2012 20:57:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 16 May 2012 12:04:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
