ogy, we have been able to establish\nwhether the modifications induced in the new cosmological picture were due to\nthe particular nature of the dynamical dark energy or a straightforward\nconsequence of the cosmological parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 May 2012 13:37:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 Sep 2013 11:23:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
