\\xi. In\nthis sense homogeneous dislocation nucleation should be understood as a\nquasi-local phenomenon.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 May 2012 14:01:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-05-09"}
